but honestly, unless you're using

00:07:47.610 --> 00:07:49.140
the Pro iPhone's camera features,

00:07:49.140 --> 00:07:50.910
there's almost nobody
here buying this phone

00:07:50.910 --> 00:07:53.130
that's gonna actually need
fast data transfer anyway

00:07:53.130 --> 00:07:55.050
so I guess you can give it a pass.

