they print the model
number inside the port.

00:08:07.800 --> 00:08:09.240
So Apple really loves hiding this

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.500
in the most discreet way possible.

00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:11.790
You know, I should really
gives some appreciation

00:08:11.790 --> 00:08:14.580
to some of the clever software
features on the iPhone 15

00:08:14.580 --> 00:08:17.430
because you could actually
consider them new.

00:08:17.430 --> 00:08:19.770
So they added stuff like
an ultra-wideband chip

00:08:19.770 --> 00:08:22.470
so you can find your phone
more easily with an Apple Watch

00:08:22.470 --> 00:08:25.277
or be found on Find My
Friends, that's new.

00:08:25.277 --> 00:08:28.080
They also added these clever audio effects

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:30.480
and video effects at an OS level,

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:32.220
so they work inside of any app.

00:08:32.220 --> 00:08:34.530
So you can be on a phone
call or a video call

00:08:34.530 --> 00:08:36.450
or a Google Meet or Zoom or whatever,

