00:10:47.970 --> 00:10:51.540
Same processing cores, same
image signal processor,

00:10:51.540 --> 00:10:55.140
same neural engine, same
A16 Bionic, same everything.

00:10:55.140 --> 00:10:58.610
So why is this new 24 megapixel default

00:10:58.610 --> 00:11:03.610
only coming to the newest iPhone
15 and not last year's Pro?

